{"tid":208841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(全能既連登仔)想搵返好耐前既網絡小說","createTime":"2017-04-19T19:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T13:12:11.000Z","uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"793a5da4f3e63466b7ad58332ca917dfb4702bc9","tid":208841,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:48:52.000Z","msg":"好耐前睇過網絡小說，大約係199x - 200x 年出既<br />\n<br />\n大約係講主角因爲失眠，買左套遊戲返黎，戴左眼罩之後思想會進入遊戲世界，真人會訓覺。<br />\n<br />\n佢記練整藥既，有小成之後請左個NPC幫佢run 間店鋪，探完險返黎就蝕撚晒d 錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後然後唔記得咩原因，個NPC 做左佢既精靈/寵物。<br />\n<br />\n求全能既連登仔幫幫手，好想睇埋個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777e76595504831a17853f95e2333046529033f5","tid":208841,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:52:10.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6dabb10f50d2b37097495f6313a9442bcd6524a","tid":208841,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ed699ddd59358ca536f6bb8f0aa693f2c2dedd68","tid":208841,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"}]}